{"tid":420923,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(加泰獨立)消防VS警察","createTime":"2017-10-01T19:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T00:55:01.000Z","uid":119729,"like":325,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"833670bd03d205a58ec206ae1bbcbfbf3f8550f1","tid":420923,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T19:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/030758_f32cd64725749516b88e8c7386c0fc9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F030758_f32cd64725749516b88e8c7386c0fc9c.jpg&h=78163502&s={SIZE}\" />【誰站在民眾一方】<br />\n加泰舉行獨立公投，大批防暴警察前往多個票站想充公選票及票箱以阻撓投票，並與堅守票站的民眾發生推撞。有老婦遭防暴警打至頭破血流，也有人被強行抬走，警方後來更出動橡膠子彈驅散群眾，造成多人受傷。雙方警民衝突至今共造成至少400人傷。<br />\n<br />\n有當地消防員組成人鏈，擋在防暴警察前面保護民眾。但從網上片段可見，防暴警嘗試驅散人群時，亦有用警棍揮向消防員。（路透社圖片）<br />\n<br />\nFrom 蘋果"},{"pid":"2b8dd8e59e4c57d89e634576542ac1c424c72344","tid":420923,"uid":119729,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T19:09:42.000Z","msg":"有無人同我一樣睇到好熱血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ce4d310940a396f5380622df4383c2a8bf0b18","tid":420923,"uid":51474,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T19:12:03.000Z","msg":"消防佬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c120461de2ede7b10652e80d0ce234cf842ae6ff","tid":420923,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T19:12:28.000Z","msg":"加泰隆尼亞反馬亂西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b664311124d5b4d81cfd4052202561d7a61c51","tid":420923,"uid":119729,"like":165,"dislike":4,"score":161,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T19:13:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>消防佬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\